# Vite auto-loads this file for `vite build` (production mode). It points the
# GitHub Pages static demo at the DeepSeek proxy deployed on Vercel, so the
# AI-assisted intake features (CSV import, "prenda desde 0" chat) work from
# the public demo, not just local dev. No secret here - the proxy itself
# holds the NVIDIA key server-side (see api/deepseek.js); this is just its
# public URL, which is unavoidably visible in the built JS bundle anyway.
VITE_DEEPSEEK_PROXY_URL=https://techpack-ai-builder.vercel.app/api/deepseek
